        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不幸二哥归天界"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三千岁有所不知，只因孙权曾命诸葛瑾来到荆州求亲，二千岁不允，是他言道："
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“虎女焉能匹配犬子！”将诸葛瑾赶出帐去，故尔孙权设此毒计！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此！想俺二哥，既然败至麦城，为何不到上庸借兵呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀三千岁呀！二千岁也曾命末将去到上庸，搬兵求救，怎奈刘封坐观成败，"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不肯发兵，并将末将赶出帐外！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是他！"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小奴才呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来气难平，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大骂刘封小畜生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你竟胆敢不发兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他是你的什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不杀小奴才怒气怎平！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘封这小奴才，如此丧心昧良，俺老张岂肯与他干休！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，起兵前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺二哥麦城遭围困"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔手摸胸膛自思忖"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "越思越想心头恨"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廖将军为何阻拦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那刘封，有我主赐他尚方宝剑，又有九头狮子鱼耳印，三千岁此番前去，只"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕画虎不成，反类其犬也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军但放宽心，俺老张自有道理！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廖化暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂、四上手、旗牌",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵发上庸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂、四上手、旗牌",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖泣颜回〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
