    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘封",
        "四上手",
        "四文堂",
        "张飞",
        "旗牌"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四大铠、刘封同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营门战鼓响，军士赛虎狼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三千岁到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四文堂、四上手、旗牌、张飞同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见三叔父！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。一旁坐下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座！三叔父，多日不见，身体可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔的倒好。你可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿好。但不知叔父打从何处而来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱老子打从成都而来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既从成都而来，我父王身体可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你父甚是安泰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我那二叔父，现在荆州，不知身体可安泰否？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个小奴才，他倒同我装起傻来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘封，你是不知呢？还是故问！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄只有不知，哪有故问之理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你那二叔父兵败麦城，已在玉泉山归天去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘封故作惊骇。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，怎么，二叔父归天了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因孙权遣诸葛瑾前来提亲，你二叔父不允，将他赶出营外。不想那诸葛瑾在"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙权面前，搬弄是非，联合曹操，故而全军覆没了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，待侄儿发兵前去，与二叔父报仇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔父为何阻拦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且问你：你这上庸城有多少人马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现有十万雄兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有十万雄兵，却也不少，今日为叔的要帮助于你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔父帮助，必定成功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但有一件！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "必须将尚方宝剑、九头狮子鱼耳印交付俺老张，方可前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若杀退孙、曹两路兵将，三叔父还要交还侄儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是自然。看印拜过！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。刘封抱剑举印，张飞拜剑、印，刘封拔剑欲杀张飞，将剑入鞘。张飞接剑、印，刘封拜，张飞"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拔剑欲杀刘封，将剑入鞘。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "印、剑已交三叔，请三叔传令发兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来慢来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔的还有一言，要同侄儿言讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔父有何金言，当面请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱老张打从成都而来，见你父年迈，只恐不久于人世，倘若你父晏驾，这汉室"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江山，不知何人承袭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若我父王晏驾，这江山定是阿斗的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能不能！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不能？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那阿斗，年轻幼小，怎能坐得江山，他怎能得够！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿斗年幼，不能执掌江山，只怕就要让与关兴坐了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关兴正在孝服之中，不能登极即位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关兴不能，还有三叔父的儿子张苞也坐得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕这江山，就是侄儿你的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄若坐，只恐满朝文武不服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么满朝文武不服，你今既有十万雄兵，待为叔的帮助与你。倘有不服者，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即按军法从事！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若得叔父保驾，侄儿登了大宝，定封叔父一字并肩王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好好，依俺老张看来，事不宜迟，倒不如点动人马，先到成都，将你父刺死，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿就可身登大宝。你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事可以做得么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做得的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此即刻起兵前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！为叔的有一计在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何妙计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔的有一铜鼓，将你装在鼓内，就说是外国进来之宝。你父那时定要观看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为叔在旁，一鞭将鼓打开，你就一刀，将你父刺死了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好。"
